headline: University of Nebraska Wins the Abbott and Big Ten Conference's Nationwide 'We Give Blood Drive' Competition, Receives $1 Million Grant from Abbott
summary: This college football season, Abbott (NYSE: ABT) and the Big Ten put fandom and the hearts of Big Ten communities to the test with their inaugural blood donation competition, "The We Give Blood Drive."
